snippet.title: 99% CHANCE that you will DIE LAUGHING! - Super FUNNY KIDS & ANIMALS videos compilation
snippet.description:
ANIMALS and KIDS are the best COMBINATION for COMPILATION!  Enjoy this funny montage of the best slips, falls, crashes, impacts, hits, punches, fights, fails and bails!

We find the best new dank memes, bloopers, funny clips, and you laugh you lose challenges in order to create an army of fails, life awesome moments, and epic wins.  New Videos Weekly and Monthly!
